Script to copy EVE settings between characters/accounts


Requirements:

Python 3.11
esi-client


Usage:

- run util.py to create API cache database
- set your settings directory in config.py (it's in %LOCALAPPDATA%\CCP\EVE on Windows)
- run copysettings.py, enter index of the source/destination character/account when prompted

Backups will be created under "backup" in the script directory, all settings files
will be overwritten with the one you selected

If you select no source file (just press enter) nothing will be done for this step

